Package: fmolsR
Title: Transparent Fully Modified OLS in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Hridayam",
           family = "Kapila",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kapilahridayam@gmail.com")
Description: This is an undergraduate research project trying to learn how to
    implement Fully Modified OLS (FMOLS) cointegrating regression in R.
    The goal is to understand how EViews implements panel FMOLS and recreate
    it transparently for learning purposes. This is NOT a professionally
    validated econometric package - it is a learning exercise using AI assistance.
    Use with caution and validate against trusted software like EViews before
    publishing results.
